## Acceptance criteria (summary)

- DEFAULT logging matches whitelist; no extraneous INFO outside it.
- With same `PlaybackSource` and active playback, Play from main menu only opens Now Playing without scan/queue.
- After scan parameter change: if current track remains in the set ‚Äî no interruption; otherwise fallback 2.3.1 after index is ready.
- Any resize ‚Üí immediate draw.
- Playlists: Save to disk only; dirty visible in main menu.
- UI hotkeys aligned with `config.yaml` on all screens.
- Main menu: shortened labels, separate play/exit blocks, dynamic width.
- Legacy config per sec. 3.
- Re-entry / sec. 2.3: fingerprint match without blocking scan (sec. 8.4); first Play may follow FIX-004 until a separate decision.

